Kottwitz's book is a resource for prospective \LaTeX{} users. It is
an ideal crash course for self-study. This book gives them all the
basics they need to get started and then make an informed decision
whether they want to continue their \LaTeX{} journey. For a beginner,
this book answers the crucial question of how to get started using
\LaTeX{} and thus serves as a much-needed guide to the jungle of
resources out there.
